Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:126836,128296}{\i1}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.38,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:128296,131383}{\i1}Yes. That's the essence of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:15.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:131383,135345}{\i1}It's not about the words you use.\NIt's not even about the technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:19.68,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:135345,139683}{\i1}It's in the way you let your\Nown emotions flow through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:24.39,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:139683,144396}{\i1}That's precisely what has moved\Nthe forgotten jazz pianist, Bill Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:27.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:145480,147107}{\i1}Finally, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:30.77,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:147107,150777}{\i1}They finally recognized you\Nas a real singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:41.28,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:153154,161288}{\t(6134,8134,4,\1c&H101010&\3c&H101010&\4c&H101010&)\fad(0,200)}— Episode 19 —\NA Long Way Up{NOTE:第19話\\N遠い歌手への道}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:01.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:177846,181266}Good morning, sir.\NYou called for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:181266,183268}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.22,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:183268,186229}You sang until very late last night.\NYou must be really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:11.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:186229,191109}No, not at all. Anyhow, I'd like to thank you\Nfor coming all the way to listen to my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:15.61,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:191109,195614}In fact, that is precisely what\NI wanted to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:19.78,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:198825,199784}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:199784,201369}Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:203955,206124}You did very well last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:206124,207500}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:207876,210295}Maybe I'm not formal enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:210295,213506}But you have to understand,\Ncompliments have never been my forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:213923,215091}Compliments?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.01,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:216801,218011}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:42.51,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:218011,222515}You've reached as my student\Nthe level I had always hoped for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.31,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:222515,225310}No, it's even higher than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:225310,226269}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:51.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:227729,231274}I think you're ready to make\Nyour debut if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:231941,233610}Debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:54.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:233610,234653}I can make my debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:235236,236237}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:236237,238239}We'll make your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:238239,239658}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:12.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:247082,252420}{\i1}Nozomi, you silly girl… as soon as you heard\Nabout the debut, you cried with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:17.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:252420,257342}You have endured far too much\Nsuffering for a seventeen-year-old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.01,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:257342,260011}However, age does not count\Ntowards becoming a good singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:23.64,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:260011,263640}All the misfortune you've experienced\Nthus far doesn't matter either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:263640,266559}What matters is that\Nyou've chosen the way of singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.97,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:266559,268978}What kind of singer\Nwill you become?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.81,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:268978,271815}The answer to that question\Nwill shape your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.48,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:271815,274484}From now on, everything\Nis in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.69,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:274484,277696}And that's what I wanted you\Nto think about through my teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.15,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:277696,280156}You see, the debut in itself\Nis not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:43.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:280156,283702}People all over the world\Nmake their debuts every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:283702,286121}You're just another one in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:46.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:286121,286830}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:287956,290834}Sir… Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:293920,295422}However, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:295422,297716}This is where things\Nwill get really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:01.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:297716,301052}It doesn't take much effort\Nto make a living as a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:04.59,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:301052,304597}But it's a different thing altogether\Nif you want to become a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.68,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:304597,306683}The real battle begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:306683,308351}I'm betting a lot on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:308351,310520}Do your best.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:11.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:310520,311688}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:16.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:312355,316025}I have to let my family know.\NI can't wait to see their reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.28,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:322907,324284}Anyway, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:29.20,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:324284,329205}Pops got discharged safe and sound and\Nyou're becoming a star. It's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.33,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:331958,335336}It was possible only\Nthanks to everyone's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:41.05,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:336045,341050}Nozomi, you better not disappoint Mr. Egawa\Nafter he's supported you for so long. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:341384,344012}Here's to No. 1 singer in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:49.97,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:344387,349976}What? With my support, you'll become the greatest\Nsinger in the whole nation, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:54.31,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:351436,354314}It's your support that\Nworries me, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.85,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:354314,357859}Hah, now you're just teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:02.86,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:358693,362864}Anyway, make sure to eat a lot today.\NYou've deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.24,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:363531,365241}We'll support you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.86,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:365241,366868}Good luck, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:368161,369370}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:370497,372499}Don't strain yourself, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.83,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:373750,375835}Oh, I'm fine, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.21,Default,Mine Shinsuke,0,0,0,,{TIME:375835,379214}I'll do my best, too. I don't want\Nto lose to my beautiful daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.63,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:379214,382634}That's the spirit!\NTime for another round… oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:383134,386262}That's not right.\NDad still needs to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:29.26,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:386262,389265}Oh, don't be so stiff.\NJust one round.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:389265,390558}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.89,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:393603,394896}I had it coming, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:396439,399901}Wow, the moon is so big.\NIt's full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:40.90,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:399901,400902}So big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.44,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:400902,402445}It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:47.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:403655,407492}{\i1}Soon I too will join the ranks\Nof professional singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:407492,410829}{\i1}I can't believe it.\NI finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.59,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:425385,426594}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:10.59,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:427011,430598}That's still not it. How many times\Ndo I need to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.76,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:431140,433768}I told you, spread your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.60,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:433768,436604}Move your head,\Nmake your hair move like waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:20.19,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:437105,440191}Move your legs lightly,\Nlike a ballerina. Now, let's repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:29.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:445530,449909}{\i1}She's ran for like half a kilometer\Njust for a few photos in some magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.62,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:452954,454622}Alright, stay in that spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.71,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:455123,458710}Imagine you're like a balloon,\Nflying up to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.62,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:458710,460628}Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:46.13,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:464048,466134}That's all wrong!\NGo back to the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.14,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:473516,475143}No, no. Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.64,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:477270,479647}What are you doing?\NGet up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:03.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:480732,483651}{\i1}But all this has nothing to do\Nwith the profession of a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:493328,497415}I spent the entire morning running around.\NAnything more and I'd have fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:498541,500793}You didn't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.42,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:500793,503421}No. I can't afford to be so capricious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:504756,506633}I'm a commercial product.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.96,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:506633,508968}I have to make sure I sell well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.84,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:508968,511846}To take advantage of every\Nopportunity that comes my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.35,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:512972,516351}Otherwise, I can't even dream\Nof becoming a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:43.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:519228,523441}Oh, by the way. I heard that you're going\Nto make your debut soon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:523441,524609}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:525276,527236}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.78,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:527236,530782}But since I've been already there,\Nlet me give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:55.49,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:530782,535495}Forget all that sweet talk about the essence\Nof music. You need to sell first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:58.62,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:535495,538623}Because if you don't, you can't\Ncall yourself a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:541584,544504}{\i1}Music that sells…\NIs that how professionals think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.69,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:561688,564691}Here, look. It's Mori Shin'ichi\Nand Ishida Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.69,Default,Mori Shin'ichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:565441,568695}You were great yesterday,\NAyumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.69,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:568695,570697}Make up room{NOTE:化粧室}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:571614,573533}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:574033,575201}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.70,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:579205,580707}On-air{NOTE:本番}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.01,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:596639,598016}{\i1}I'm a commercial product.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:09.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:604022,609777}{\i1}But I feel that since her debut\NMiki-san's been too busy to actually sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.69,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:604605,608693}{\fad(1500,0)}Kōda Miki Autograph Session{NOTE:香田美紀サイン会}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:20.37,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:616242,620371}Kōda Miki's First Single\N"The Wounded Bird"{NOTE:デビュー曲\\Nとべない小鳩}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.50,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:628463,629505}Okay, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.79,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:629505,631799}Good job. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.17,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:631799,633176}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:634010,635720}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:42.60,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:638890,642602}{\i1}Miki was already a budding singer.\NUpon hearing her words,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:47.19,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:642602,647190}{\i1}Nozomi felt great uneasiness and\Nanxiety creeping into her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:51.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:647190,651736}{\i1}The anxiety was slowly, but steadily\Nspreading, like a rain cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:663331,666626}{\i1}Miki-san has her own fans already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:666626,668878}{\i1}She's quickly climbing\Nthe ladder of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:669712,670546}{\i1}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:673091,674801}Step on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.97,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:679889,681974}Ah, what a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:681974,685645}They have wrinkled my new dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:685645,689148}Nozomi-san, what's next\Non the schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:689148,690525}Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:691818,693611}Oh no, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:693611,695321}You have a lesson with Mr. Egawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:695321,698908}but at the same time an autograph session\Nin a newly opened record store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:698908,700535}It was my agent who scheduled it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.66,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:702829,704664}Alright. Drive me to that store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:45.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:704664,705873}What about the lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:50.46,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:707083,710461}I'll just have to catch up\Nbefore my new song comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:55.13,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:710461,715133}But the autograph session gets priority as it'll\Nboost my sales. That's how you become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:717969,720388}You'd like to see\NMr. Egawa, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:08.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:723307,728646}That's fine. You can go and tell on me as you\Nalways do, if that's what you want, Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:729272,730648}I've never badmouthed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.48,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:732233,733484}Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:733484,735903}Anyway, I need a little space now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.78,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:736737,738781}Your work is done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:738781,740158}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:46.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:761762,766684}{\i1}It's obvious that Miki-san chose\Nthe quickest way to get to famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:53.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:766684,773399}{\i1}But because of that, she must devote all\Nher time to her promotion and public relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:57.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:773399,777653}{\i1}She will certainly become a star,\Nbut can she call herself a real singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:777653,779655}{\i1}Is this how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:54.40,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:767935,774400}Egawa
Comment: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:03.71,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:783718,783718}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:787388,789348}Kōda decided to miss her lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:791642,794270}Did you come here\Njust to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.98,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:794979,796981}You could've just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:796981,798524}Yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:798524,800109}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:800109,802528}In any event,\NI don't intend to criticize Kōda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:27.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:802904,807533}Her packed schedule only proves\Nthat she is selling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:808242,812538}But sir, don't you think her technique\Nwill worsen if she keeps skipping lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:812872,814040}Of course it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:814040,817293}But if she manages to hold for a year or two,\Nit will already be quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:817293,820421}Do not forget that new singers\Narrive on the market every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:822423,824050}This means that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:48.97,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:824425,828971}Yes. If you're not very careful, you'll end up\Nlike every other consumable good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:828971,832433}There is only one way to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.01,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:832433,835019}You have to plan ahead\Non how you're going to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.60,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:835019,837605}You can't lose sight of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:838439,840608}Can't lose sight of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:06.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:841150,846238}In other words, keep singing\Nwith all your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:847031,849533}It's difficult in the long run, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:849533,851035}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:15.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:851035,855706}Instead of wasting time here with me, I think you'd\Nbe better off going back to the club in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:857750,858501}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.68,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:878396,879689}That's the girl from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.14,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:879689,881148}Did she come to sing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.35,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:881148,882358}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.79,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:898207,901794}Hey, Bill! She's here again!\NPlay us something good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.79,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:901794,903796}Hey, miss! Sing for us once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:905006,907258}{\i1}Everyone remembers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.17,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:909385,911178}I was sure you'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.72,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:911178,913723}Here, get on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:17.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:913723,917226}Nitta-san, I'm very happy,\Nbut today I'd prefer not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.73,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:917226,920730}What are you talking about?\NEveryone's looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.14,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:920730,923149}Especially Bill.\NHe's been coming here every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:55.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:946464,955181}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I want a chain of love to capture you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I want to tie you and not let you go  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:16:02.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:955181,962855}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  For you to always stay by me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Morning, evening, all night long  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:10.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:962855,970696}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  For us to live together  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:21.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:972448,981040}{\an8\fad(0,2000)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  If somebody was to sell one now  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I would buy it no matter the cost  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:974200,977036}{\i1}It's no good.\NI've lost all my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:977036,979955}{\i1}I can't sing naturally.\NThe words don't flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.92,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:985461,986921}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.98,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:986921,987980}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.30,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:988923,991300}What's wrong, Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:991300,992968}It's all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.97,Default,Bill Jones,0,0,0,,{TIME:994220,995971}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:41.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:997598,1001018}I'm sorry, but I can't.\NI'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.31,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001393,1003312}– What's wrong?\N– Hey! Mine-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.15,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006107,1009151}Nozomi-chan…\NWhat in the world has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019620,1023874}{\i1}It was a complete disaster.\NWhat a resounding failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:08.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023874,1028838}{\i1}I disappointed all those people.\NThey were looking forward to it so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.84,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034385,1035845}Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036554,1038222}Nitta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038222,1039849}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:23.64,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039849,1043644}Wait a moment. If you want to ask for an advice\Nabout life, I'm afraid I'm not the best person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043644,1045229}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:27.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045229,1047565}I just don't understand\Nthings anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047565,1050151}What is music all about?\NWhy do I want to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.31,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050151,1051318}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:36.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052111,1056740}Mr. Egawa told me that\NI'm ready to make my debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.90,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056740,1058909}Oh, that's a good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:45.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058909,1065332}But I wonder, if I become a professional now,\Nis that enough to call myself a real singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.34,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072798,1075342}I don't know all the answers, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:18:01.34,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076218,1081348}This is actually the reason\Nwhy I'm going on a journey again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:02.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081849,1082933}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082933,1084351}Another journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:11.27,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085686,1091275}I met you again in Yokohama and I saw how\Nyou brought about the great Bill Jones' comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.86,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091275,1092860}It was a huge shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:19.36,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094278,1099366}My biggest dream would be to play\Nthe trumpet the way he can play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.57,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099909,1101577}That's why I feel depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102620,1104455}Nitta-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:28.70,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104455,1108709}So far I have continued to play the trumpet\Nwithout having a clear purpose in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.37,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108709,1112379}I've been looking for one for years.\NBut now I feel that I'm on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:45.22,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120221,1125226}I hope that someday we will meet again.\NBut I have a hunch you'll be a big star by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.85,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125226,1126852}Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129313,1132358}Despite so much experience,\Nhe went on a journey to find his purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132358,1133776}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133776,1136237}Now I know what I'm singing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137780,1140366}Nitta-san, you taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140366,1142243}Thank you, Nitta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.62,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149291,1151627}You want to quit?\NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151627,1153087}Yes. I know it's short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153087,1155214}I won't hide it's a hassle for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155214,1158884}Oh, well, I guess I don't mind, since there\Nare countless people willing to be my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.84,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158884,1161845}That means you'll finally get\Nto focus on studying. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:25.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161845,1165557}Actually, no. After our discussion here,\NI'm going to say goodbye to Mr. Egawa as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166308,1167726}What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.93,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167726,1169937}What about your dream\Nof becoming a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169937,1171981}I'm going to look\Nfor my own way of achieving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171981,1174066}Oh? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:38.32,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174066,1178320}I don't think the show business world is so nice\Nthat you can become a singer all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178320,1180406}Oh, well. Good luck, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183409,1184576}Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187288,1189415}{\i1}What is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.83,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189415,1191834}{\i1}At any rate this means\None less rival to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194962,1196714}You want to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:02.46,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198674,1202469}Nozomi. Before I say anything,\NI want to know the reason for this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:05.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202469,1205973}I'm not so sure if I have what it takes\Nto be a professional singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205973,1207808}That's not a good reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.39,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207808,1209393}Tell me what's really on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.31,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209393,1211312}What is the actual reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211312,1214898}Sir… There's something\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:18.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216608,1218610}What is music?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220362,1222323}That's… something\Nyou can't explain with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:28.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223032,1228329}At the beginning, I envied Miki-san for\Nhow fast she was climbing the career ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:34.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229121,1234335}But as time passes, I'm under the impression\Nthat she has less and less to do with actual music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:40.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235252,1240341}Even if I debut and become a star,\NI don't want to end up being like Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:44.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241008,1244345}So are you saying that\Nyou don't want to become a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:46.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244636,1246847}No. Far from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:52.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246847,1252936}But I don't want to become someone\Nwho is blinded by money and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254146,1256148}My dad told me once that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:21:01.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256148,1261695}as a singer, my is job to comfort\Npeople who are in low spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:05.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262488,1265699}Before becoming a star,\NI'd like to become such singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.24,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266575,1268243}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:11.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268243,1271705}If that's what you want,\Nyou're free leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272623,1273832}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:19.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273832,1279713}But know that you have chosen a much harder path\Nthan the one that leads you to become a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.25,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280756,1282257}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.71,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282257,1285719}Nozomi-chan!\NAre you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:30.18,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286261,1290182}You were so close\Nof achieving your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290182,1293727}Thank you for worrying\Nabout me, Sune-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293727,1296980}But as long as we have something to eat,\NI think my family will get by somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296980,1298690}Good bye, Sune-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.23,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299942,1301235}Nozomi-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.44,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301693,1303445}Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:49.24,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305864,1309243}Nozomi has grown even more\Nthan I had realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:53.24,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309701,1313247}She's finally understood\Nwhat music is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.62,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313789,1316625}Nozomi, you're going to be\Nall alone from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:59.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316625,1319253}You don't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:03.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319586,1323882}You figured everything out all by yourself.\NYou really are something, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326051,1328095}{\i1}That's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:13.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328095,1333267}{\i1}I'm a singer.\NThis is what I'm going to do in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:16.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333267,1336019}{\i1}I have to sing\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.36,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1341567,1344361}{\fad(0,2000)}Station Store{NOTE:駅前商店}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1378395,1381982}{\i1}I don't know what\Nmom and dad will say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:05.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381982,1385652}{\i1}But I'm determined and\Nnothing will change my mind now.
Comment: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:17.99,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1397990,1397990}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:22.87,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399992,1402870}{\i1}Fanni comes back from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:28.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1402870,1408625}{\i1}Nozomi wonders whether rejecting\Nthe opportunity for a debut was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:31.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408625,1411712}{\i1}She goes to ask Fanni for guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:35.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411712,1415883}{\i1}But for some reason,\NFanni doesn't want to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:41.01,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415883,1421013}{\i1}Shortly thereafter, she learns from Miki\Nthat Fanni is actually her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:46.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421013,1426101}{\i1}It turns out to be a fatal blow\Nand Nozomi disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:51.02,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1426101,1431023}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Welcome Back, Fanni".
